  </div>
  <div class="font-fraunces primary-clr text-3xl md:text-6xl text-center py-6 md:py-10 pt-5 medium tracking-tight leading-10 lg:leading-12 w-full max-w-[800px] md:max-w-[1100px] lg:max-w-[900px] lg:h-max-[307px] mx-auto text-clip overflow-hidden"
  style="line-height: 1.5;">Discover the charm of Thalassery at The Heritage 1866. Your unforgettable experience awaits!</div>
